31:17.692 --> 31:20.295
Fancy seeing you here.

31:20.375 --> 31:21.656
- Hey, Zoey.

31:21.736 --> 31:23.097
Come here often?

31:23.177 --> 31:25.139
- It's not a big whoop,

31:25.220 --> 31:28.102
but, you know,
I am a VIP member.

31:28.182 --> 31:30.305
