31:52.166 --> 31:53.608
- Oh, yeah, well,
he can be a little

31:53.688 --> 31:55.290
door-slammy sometimes.

31:55.370 --> 31:58.172
- Must be hard understanding
some of this kids stuff.

31:58.253 --> 32:00.895
Hey!

32:00.975 --> 32:02.337
- Hey
- This is Zoey.

32:02.417 --> 32:03.378
- I like your fox.

32:03.458 --> 32:04.539
- His name's Marvin.

32:04.619 --> 32:05.580
- It's a good name.

32:05.660 --> 32:07.342
Hey, Perry,

32:07.422 --> 32:09.544
do you know what noise
