33:54.929 --> 33:56.931
- It's fine, it's fine,
it's just--

33:59.694 --> 34:01.576
I just feel like you've
been acting a little weird,

34:01.656 --> 34:04.178
and I don't know
if something's going on?

34:05.380 --> 34:07.382
- Oh, um...

34:12.146 --> 34:14.148
It's just...

34:16.791 --> 34:19.634
- Okay.

34:19.714 --> 34:21.596
- Opening up
isn't easy for me.

34:21.676 --> 34:23.237
- Mm-hmm.

34:23.317 --> 34:27.522
- And in the past,
sometimes I shared too much

34:27.602 --> 34:30.324
too soon,
and I don't want to do that.

34:30.405 --> 34:32.206
So...

34:32.286 --> 34:35.089
