39:47.241 --> 39:48.402
is what triggered
the song switching,

39:48.482 --> 39:49.443
so this whole thing
has been your fault

39:49.523 --> 39:50.885
from the very beginning.

39:50.965 --> 39:52.767
- Eh, I would have
said it nicer myself, but--

39:52.847 --> 39:54.088
- Zoey.

39:54.168 --> 39:55.569
I have been doing this

39:55.649 --> 39:57.251
a little longer than you, okay?

39:57.331 --> 39:59.373
So here's what I know.

39:59.453 --> 40:02.016
