connect this week.

40:24.839 --> 40:26.640
You sent me all these
text messages--

40:26.720 --> 40:28.242
- Oh, gosh, did I?

40:28.322 --> 40:29.603
Bored at work, I guess.
Sorry.

40:29.683 --> 40:31.846
- Oh, no-no, no, I loved it.

40:31.926 --> 40:34.288
I watched the panda licking
the popsicle video

40:34.368 --> 40:36.130
a hundred times.

40:36.210 --> 40:38.933
I just, um...

40:40.054 --> 40:42.777
How have you been doing?

40:42.857 --> 40:44.338
Is everything all right?

40:44.418 --> 40:46.420
- Everything's fine.

40:47.902 --> 40:50.825
[uplifting music]

40:50.905 --> 40:53.828
♪ ♪

40:53.908 --> 40:56.190
♪ All I want to do when
I wake up in the morning ♪

40:56.270 --> 40:58.993
♪ Is see your eyes ♪

40:59.073 --> 41:02.076
♪ Rosanna, Rosanna ♪

41:02.156 --> 41:04.678
♪ I never thought
that a girl like you ♪

41:04.758 --> 41:07.441
♪ Could ever care for me ♪

41:07.521 --> 41:09.523
♪ Rosanna ♪

41:10.684 --> 41:13.487
- Max's song.

41:13.567 --> 41:15.729
♪ All I want to do
in the middle of the evening ♪

41:15.810 --> 41:18.412
♪ Is hold you tight ♪

41:18.492 --> 41:20.574
♪ Rosanna, Rosanna ♪

41:20.654 --> 41:22.536
- Emily.

41:22.616 --> 41:24.418
Emily, Emily.

41:24.498 --> 41:26.300
I'm sorry.

41:26.380 --> 41:28.542
I'm sorry I wasn't
hearing you before.

41:28.622 --> 41:30.464
I wasn't paying attention
the way that I should have,

41:30.544 --> 41:31.826
but I am now, okay?

41:31.906 --> 41:34.228
I'm here.
I'm right here with you.

41:35.629 --> 41:38.112
- ♪ Anyone ♪

41:38.192 --> 41:41.715
♪ Please send me anyone ♪

41:41.795 --> 41:45.399
