41:45.479 --> 41:49.283
♪ I need someone ♪

41:49.363 --> 41:52.406
♪ Oh, anyone ♪

41:52.486 --> 41:56.410
♪ Please send me anyone ♪

41:56.490 --> 42:00.094
♪ Lord, is there anyone? ♪

42:00.174 --> 42:04.298
♪ I need someone ♪

42:04.378 --> 42:07.181
♪ A hundred million stories ♪

42:07.261 --> 42:08.662
♪ And a hundred million songs ♪

42:08.742 --> 42:11.625
♪ I feel stupid when I sing ♪

42:11.705 --> 42:15.389
♪ Nobody's listening to me ♪

42:15.469 --> 42:18.392
♪ Nobody's listening ♪

42:18.472 --> 42:19.673
- It's okay.

42:19.753 --> 42:21.435
I'm listening.

